-- 2nd point to note is that after 12 points in the Arch abilites you have access to the class ones, which may prove to help you more in the long run.<br>
-- Personally I would have recomended that you stop at CF1, the improvment in crits is nice for CF2, but not a great upgrade.<br>
-- Since you've all ready spent those points, in CF2, I would recomend that you skip CA and don't get ND3, stop at ND2.  That way you can get to the class abilities sooner.  You can always go back and get the Arch abilities your missing out on later, after you pick up the class ones you want.<br>
