Innate Run Speed 3<br>
Innate Regeneration 3<br>
Natural Durability 3<br>
Chaotic Stab<br>
<br>
Those would be where I put the first slew of points, since I deal with not being able to get to a mob's back due to positioning on mobs. Plus with the stupid high ac and hitting for 1, 1, 1, 2, 12, etc, it's nice to add in that 120, once in a while. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukelcekindredsouls.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KelceKindredsouls</A> at: 5/26/02 5:49:06 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uelandileldaron.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elandil Eldaron</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/27/02 2:52:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8844.topic&index=173>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The way to go</span><hr size=1> Why i asked this is that maybe what we do best is Damage, i agree with this, but the point is that i maybe prefer upgrading some of disadvantages of rogues.<br>
